    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <placeName>Baltimore</placeName>
                <date>Decr 18<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1832</date>
            </p>
            <p>Dear <addressee>Isaac</addressee></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I recd your letter for <persName>Mr Cohen</persName> I should have
                been happy to see<lb/> that your Health was better than it seems to be but by taking
                care I hope<lb/> you will be better this winter than you have been we are thank
                god<lb/> all well I have told <persName>Miss Seixas</persName> what you said in
                regard of <persName>Miss<lb/> Nathan</persName> I have nothing new to write but I
                wish you to let me know<lb/> why <persName>Mr Peixotto</persName> does not wish to
                have your letters directed to his care<lb/> should it be on acct of <persName>Miss
                    Simah</persName>, and I think for reason I have<lb/> it is on that out from some
                information I have had on that<lb/> acct let me know it by next Post I also would
                advise you not to<lb/>
                <sic>to</sic> visit too often During the <sic>Absent</sic> of <persName>Mr
                    Peixotto</persName> at his House<lb/> when I receive your answer I shall be more
                particular till then I wish<lb/> you not to say any thing to anybody about it, and
                    <sic>depent</sic> on it I <sic>feell</sic><lb/> as much <sic>intrested</sic> on
                your acct with what ever depends on your<lb/>
                <sic>Happiness</sic> as on any what can entrust are in this world</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I remain your friend <persName role="author">Zalma
                Rehine</persName></p>
            <p>all the <sic>familia</sic> send their love to you</p>
            <pb n="4"/>
            <p>the <sic><addressee>revd Isaac Leeser</addressee></sic></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>No. 86 Walnut Street</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>single</p>
        </body>
